nodes.text: Brine-eels were a large non-sentient species of eel that lived in salt water.

A species of eel, brine-eel had powerful jaws and were used in warfare. In 23 ABY when Jedi apprentice Jaina Solo heard a whining, gnawing sound that was an Imperial Assault Shuttle breaching the hull of GemDiver Station; she likened the sound to a huge battle-ready brine-eel chewing its way through the station's armor.
